title: Tacoma school board candidates at Rotary forum
text:
Tacoma school board candidates at Rotary forum 
By Debbie Cafazzo Order Reprint of this Story 
The public is invited to hear candidates for Tacoma School Board speak at a meeting of Rotary Club of Tacoma No. 8 on Thursday Oct. 22. 
The meeting starts at 12:10 pm. in the Plaza Grand Ballroom of the Landmark Convention Center, 47 St. Helens Ave., Tacoma. A lunch buffet is available for $20. 
There is limited free parking across the street from the center. 
Debbie Cafazzo: 253-597-8635
